casebody.data:
Rebekah GEE, Secretary, Louisiana Department of Health and Hospitals, Petitioner
v.
JUNE MEDICAL SERVICES L.L.C., et al. No. 18-1460 Supreme Court of the United States. October 4, 2019

The petition for writ of certiorari is granted. The case is consolidated and a total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
